with frame detailm no-labels no-box no-underline down stream-io width 80.

form
    disp-frt at 1
    xar-inv.freight format "->,>>9.99" at 11
    xar-inv.tax-amt format "->,>>9.99" at 21
    v-net to 43 format "->,>>>,>>9.99"
